Package cs2810.group30.oaxacabackend.models

package cs2810.group30.oaxacabackend.models
Models Component are the class files which contain the @Entity annotation representing data that can be persisted to the database. An entity represents a table stored in a database. Every instance of an entity represents a row in the table.
